at around 11:00 PM

15
00:01:23,580 --> 00:01:24,700
on June 6, 2023,

16
00:01:24,980 --> 00:01:26,470
the defendant, Li Songyan,

17
00:01:26,470 --> 00:01:28,350
was caught driving without a license

18
00:01:28,360 --> 00:01:29,700
and under the influence of alcohol

19
00:01:29,710 --> 00:01:31,390
on Longshan Road,
Nancheng District, Qinzhong.

20
00:01:31,500 --> 00:01:33,670
When stopped

21
00:01:33,670 --> 00:01:34,830
by traffic officer Li Guomin,

22
00:01:34,840 --> 00:01:36,460
he refused to cooperate,
resisted law enforcement,

23
00:01:36,470 --> 00:01:39,340
and engaged in a physical struggle,
resulting in injuries to Li Guomin's

24
00:01:39,340 --> 00:01:40,340
wrist and fingers.

25
00:01:40,350 --> 00:01:41,490
According to the assessment,

26
00:01:41,580 --> 00:01:42,910
Li Guomin's injuries

27
00:01:42,920 --> 00:01:44,300
were classified as minor injuries.

28
00:01:44,390 --> 00:01:45,410
This office believes that

29
00:01:45,980 --> 00:01:47,390
the defendant Li Songyan

30
00:01:47,420 --> 00:01:50,140
obstructed law enforcement officers
performing their official duties,

31
00:01:51,140 --> 00:01:52,580
constituting the crime
of obstructing public service.

32
00:01:52,580 --> 00:01:55,210
However, considering that he was
under 18 at the time of the crime,

33
00:01:55,220 --> 00:01:56,550
was a first-time offender,

34
00:01:57,390 --> 00:02:00,220
and has actively compensated the victim
and obtained forgiveness,

35
00:02:00,220 --> 00:02:02,330
he meets the criteria
for conditional non-prosecution

36
00:02:02,330 --> 00:02:03,260
and has shown remorse.

37
00:02:03,270 --> 00:02:05,400
Based on Article 282, Paragraph One

38
00:02:05,400 --> 00:02:07,980
of the Criminal Procedure Law
of the People's Republic of China,

39
00:02:08,110 --> 00:02:09,390
this office has decided

40
00:02:09,420 --> 00:02:10,860
to grant conditional non-prosecution.

41
00:02:11,220 --> 00:02:14,180
The probation period is six months,
during which he mustn't leave the city.

42
00:02:14,190 --> 00:02:14,750
Additionally,

43
00:02:15,030 --> 00:02:17,070
due to the guardianship
deficiency issues

44
00:02:17,070 --> 00:02:18,590
reflected in the investigation report,

45
00:02:18,980 --> 00:02:20,070
a Supervisory Order

46
00:02:20,070 --> 00:02:21,900
will be issued to his guardians,

47
00:02:22,390 --> 00:02:23,580
requiring them to receive

48
00:02:23,900 --> 00:02:25,070
family education guidance.

49
00:02:25,740 --> 00:02:27,790
Qinzhong Nancheng District
People's Procuratorate,

50
00:02:27,790 --> 00:02:29,790
June 18, 2023.

51
00:02:30,300 --> 00:02:31,140
You may be seated.

52
00:02:37,550 --> 00:02:38,180
Li Songyan.

53
00:02:38,580 --> 00:02:40,270
Due to your weak legal awareness

54
00:02:40,280 --> 00:02:41,170
and impulsive actions,

55
00:02:41,270 --> 00:02:42,420
you broke the law.

56
00:02:42,830 --> 00:02:44,300
I hope you'll cherish this opportunity

57
00:02:44,300 --> 00:02:45,890
(Prosecutor)
for conditional non-prosecution.

58
00:02:45,900 --> 00:02:47,700
Accept correction and education,

59
00:02:47,700 --> 00:02:49,680
regain confidence,
and look forward to the future.

60
00:02:49,690 --> 00:02:51,580
(Defendant)

61
00:02:51,580 --> 00:02:52,230
Sure.

62
00:02:52,740 --> 00:02:53,950
I understand my mistake.

63
00:02:54,270 --> 00:02:55,300
I'll correct myself.

64
00:02:58,270 --> 00:02:58,860
Li Hai.

65
00:02:59,140 --> 00:03:00,070
In reality, parents are

66
00:03:00,110 --> 00:03:01,790
a child's first teachers.

67
00:03:02,140 --> 00:03:03,860
The family is also
a child's first school,

68
00:03:04,140 --> 00:03:07,020
and the first line of defense
against juvenile delinquency.

69
00:03:07,150 --> 00:03:09,180
No matter what stage
a child is at in their growth,

70
00:03:09,580 --> 00:03:11,860
they always need emotional care
from their parents.

71
00:03:12,670 --> 00:03:14,390
Stop using blame as a form of concern.

72
00:03:16,830 --> 00:03:17,580
Alright.

73
00:03:18,110 --> 00:03:18,980
Thank you, prosecutor.

74
00:03:19,460 --> 00:03:20,980
