get into a boarding school

85
00:03:49,180 --> 00:03:50,550
in the city where her father works.

86
00:03:51,580 --> 00:03:53,670
A new environment, a fresh start.

87
00:03:53,860 --> 00:03:55,140
It's a good thing for her.

88
00:03:57,670 --> 00:03:59,140
The dark clouds will pass,

89
00:03:59,790 --> 00:04:01,670
and the sun will shine again.

90
